query:
SELECT 
  po.id,
  po.orderNumber,
  po.customerOrderNumber,
  po.shippingStatus,
  COUNT(poi.id) as totalItems
FROM pickingOrders po
LEFT JOIN pickingOrderItems poi ON poi.pickingOrderId = po.id
WHERE po.shippingStatus = 'invoice_linked'
GROUP BY po.id, po.orderNumber, po.customerOrderNumber, po.shippingStatus
LIMIT 5;
